Scatterblaster:


Doing a quick aerial maneuver, three shots struck his armor, or rather, the 
dead frame of a robot he wore as extra armor.  "You'll have to do better than 
that fool!" he yelled, firing off ten explosive rounds downward at Wespah, 
getting ready to pull out the big stuff in case of emergency.
